title: Episode 144: Moving Day
description:
Ms. Pat is moving out of Plainfield, IN and to Atlanta on the same day her show moves to Paramount Plus. Check it out now as well as her Netflix special "Y'All Wanna Hear Something Crazy?" on February 8.
